(EmpathRAG currently has a large Reddit-based retrieval corpus. That corpus is) Tj
T*
(useful for research comparison and ablation, but it should not be the primary) Tj
T*
(student-facing support source for a mental-health-adjacent demo.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
